# JJ Media - Project Context & Rules

## Project Stack
- PHP (Backend)
- Tailwind CSS (Frontend)
- PHPMailer (MMS/Email)

## File Structure
- `pages/`: Core page templates.
- `include/`: Reusable components.
- `src/`: Tailwind source.
- `dist/`: Build output.

## Code Standards
- Use Tailwind utility classes directly in PHP templates.
- Ensure responsive design (mobile-first).
- Handle form submissions via `submit_form.php` using PHPMailer.

## Commands
- Dev: `npm run dev`
- Build: `npm run build`
